# Open Voting Foundation

[[!img open-voting-foundation-logo.png alt="Open Voting Foundation logo" class="projectlogo" link="no"]]

The Open Voting Foundation aims
to educate the public and governmental officials and entities concerning
elections systems based upon open source software, and further to
promote the adoption of open source voting and elections solutions
worldwide.

